name: The Fetus
description:
A Commemoration of the First Mint on HEN by Texadelic. The Original Now Goes for Prices Far Outside Anything Affordable for this Collector. What Makes the Original Even More Unique is it Does Not Have an Official Title (I Mistakenly Put the Title in the Description).


This Version (Still in the Womb) is Mutating and Even in the Early Stages of Development it's Clear He has Big Aspirations of Growing Up and Becoming a World Famous Bagpipe Musician.


* I'll Let You in on a Little Secret. My Goal is to Buy Back One of the Originals Once I've Sold Enough Art to Pay for It.
